dct_title_s: Beirut central district : the paths of history / the archeological projects in the BCD are undertaken under the auspices of the Ministry of Culture and Higher Education, the Directorate General of Antiquities and Solidere (Archaeological map)
dct_description_sm: Title from panel. Tourist map printed in July, 1995. Map on recto shows land use and density of population. Includes text and color illustrations. Map on verso includes time spots, and time line columns.
